      "caption": "Injuries are not badges.\nInjuries are training debt.\n\nEvery 'I'll push through' is two weeks of missed training next month.\n\nToughness is not pretending.\nToughness is coming back healthy.\n\n#bjj #hardtruth #recovery #bjjlongevity",
